The paper proposes a novel deep graph neural network architecture that efficiently extracts knowledge from high-order neighbors and integrates knowledge from different hops of neighbors into the network in an AdaBoost way. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
